HEADWORD: Comparatively
<hw>Com*par"a*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>According to estimate
made by comparison; relatively; not positively or absolutely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With but <qex>comparatively</qex> few exceptions.</q>
<rj><qau>Prescott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

